      <title>国际足联主席访问美国国会讨论2026年世界杯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/fifa-president-visits-us-capitol-to-discuss-2026-world-cup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球足球管理机构主席来到美国国会大厦，与立法者讨论即将举行的 2026 年世界杯锦标赛的安全问题，以及放宽外国球迷进入美国观看比赛的事宜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/fifa-president-visits-us-capitol-to-discuss-2026-world-cup</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 18:19:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>海地任命新总理试图恢复秩序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/haiti-names-new-prime-minister-to-try-to-restore-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体报道，海地过渡委员会任命了一位新总理，试图恢复这个黑帮泛滥的国家的秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/haiti-names-new-prime-minister-to-try-to-restore-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克在大选前的鼓舞人心的演讲中寻求“最大的回归”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/sunak-seeks-greatest-comeback-in-pre-election-pep-talk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克（Rishi Sunak）在选前演讲中敦促保守党忠实人士参与“政治史上最伟大的东山再起”，这默认了首相本周在英格兰各地的地方投票中面临着巨大的胜算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/sunak-seeks-greatest-comeback-in-pre-election-pep-talk</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 16:53:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏丹角色争端加剧，阿联酋拒绝伦敦市长职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/uae-snubs-london-s-lord-mayor-as-dispute-over-sudan-role-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于波斯湾国家涉嫌在苏丹内战中所扮演的角色，阿联酋取消了与伦敦市长和其他英国官员的会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/uae-snubs-london-s-lord-mayor-as-dispute-over-sudan-role-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 16:28:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院允许德克萨斯州对色情片实施年龄验证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/supreme-court-lets-texas-enforce-porn-age-verification-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院允许德克萨斯州继续对色情网站实施年龄验证要求，驳回了一个行业领导团体的质疑，该团体认为该法律侵犯了成年人的宪法权利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/supreme-court-lets-texas-enforce-porn-age-verification-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 16:09:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱赢得众议院对阿根廷休克疗法的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/milei-wins-key-lower-house-support-for-argentina-s-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷下议院首先批准了哈维尔·米莱总统的综合法案，先是全部批准，后来又部分批准，这是这位自由主义领导人的重大胜利，他的改革现在在参议院面临更激烈的斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/milei-wins-key-lower-house-support-for-argentina-s-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚威胁开除占领大楼的学生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/columbia-student-take-over-campus-building-yale-police-clear-encampment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在哥伦比亚大学，将自己封锁在校园建筑内的学生示威者正面临被开除的危险。在耶鲁大学，警察被派去清理抗议者誓言要重新占领的一个营地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/columbia-student-take-over-campus-building-yale-police-clear-encampment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 14:36:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普提出移民拘留营、拜登起诉、《时代》报道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/trump-floats-migrant-detention-camps-biden-prosecution-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普正在考虑在可能的第二个总统任期内采取一系列政策举措，这将考验司法系统、移民法和公民权利的界限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/trump-floats-migrant-detention-camps-biden-prosecution-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 14:30:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国众议院民主党人誓言让议长约翰逊免于下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/house-democrats-vow-to-save-speaker-johnson-from-hardliner-coup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院民主党领导人表示，该党将努力使众议院议长迈克·约翰逊免受共和党强硬派发起的任何罢免行动的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/house-democrats-vow-to-save-speaker-johnson-from-hardliner-coup</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 14:29:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菅直人表示，在哈马斯做出回应之前，以色列不会加入停战谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/israel-won-t-join-truce-talks-until-hamas-responds-kan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国营的坎新闻报道，只有当哈马斯对国际调解的最新临时休战和释放人质提议做出回应时，以色列才会考虑加入与哈马斯的停火谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/israel-won-t-join-truce-talks-until-hamas-responds-kan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 10:04:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
